# Quick Start

This guide will help you get started with the project in just a few minutes.

## Installation

First, follow the [Installation Guide](installation.md) to set up the project.

## Basic Usage

```python
from {{ package_name }} import main

# Run the main function
result = main()
```

## Running the Application

```bash
# Using uv
uv run {{ package_name }}

# Or if installed in your environment
{{ package_name }}
```

